	* data/colorschemes/Makefile.am: Plugged the new colorscheme into the
		Makefile wires.

	* data/colorschemes/spiffE.xml: Added "spiff"'sh colorscheme (made out of
		fanaticism about the "SpiffE" theme for Eterm) ,-)

